snippet.title: Sokolab - Official Trailer | Steam
snippet.description:
SokoLab is a Sokoban game where you play as a cute robot! Push blocks to the objective to reach the end of the level, new mechanics are introduced throughout the game adding layers of complexity to the puzzles!

Sokolab is available on Steam!
Buy now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2357450/SokoLab/?curator_clanid=41279626
